%% PATIENT_MANAGEMENT Processing Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant HABADTE
    participant Filters
    participant Counters

    HABADTE->>Filters: Apply BR 017 file indicator zero
    Filters-->>Counters: Increment skippedFileIndicatorZero

    HABADTE->>Filters: Apply BR 018 flag void voided
    Filters-->>Counters: Increment skippedVoided

    HABADTE->>Filters: Apply BR 019 inpatient outpatient flag outpatient
    Filters-->>Counters: Increment skippedOutpatient

    HABADTE->>Counters: Increment totalRecordsRead and totalValidTransfers
